title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 217-4.2 - Prohibitions
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 217-4.2 - Prohibitions

State Regulations

No person shall operate an official emissions inspection
station using equipment and/or procedures that are not in compliance with
department procedures and/or standards. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
217-4.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
